caption: An aggressive trap metal track with distorted 808s, screamed vocals, and chaotic production. Features industrial sound design, rapid hi-hats, and a dark aggressive energy that blends hip-hop and metal influences.
lyrics:
[Intro]

Let's go!

[Verse 1]
Demon in my head won't let me sleep
Darkness running through me running deep
Everybody fake everybody lies
Watch the world burn before my eyes
Rage inside me can't contain
Fuel the fire feel the pain
Breaking chains breaking free
This is the real me

[Chorus]
Chaos! In my veins!
Chaos! Break the chains!
Chaos! Feel no pain!
Chaos!

[Verse 2]
They don't understand what I've been through
Judging from the outside with no clue
Battle scars across my soul
Lost myself but now I'm whole
Rising from the ashes of the past
Built to break but built to last
No more hiding who I am
This is my final stand

[Chorus]
Chaos! In my veins!
Chaos! Break the chains!
Chaos! Feel no pain!
Chaos!

[Breakdown]

Can't stop me now!

[Outro]
Chaos!
